// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1531 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 5b5d15ac-abac-5757-9717-54fea7002221

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.10*")
